OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny shower5s
OL,6,Fwill soon die out to leave the evening
OL,7,Fand the rest of the night dry with
OL,8,Fsome clear periods. Freshening
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly wind later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FThe morning will be dry
OL,12,Fwith some brightness. Clouding over
OL,13,Ffrom the south in the afternoon with
OL,14,Fthe chance of a little rain by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
