OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy and windy on Thursday with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, drier and less
OL,8,Fwindy later. Dry and bright on Friday
OL,9,Fand Saturday. Strengthening
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds across Shetland on
OL,11,FSaturday.
